3.8.6 Multiple Selections - The switch Statement
//若没有break,它会一直执行下去case by case until the end of switch
switch (choice){
case 1:
	. . .
	break;
case 2:
	. . .
	break;
case 3:
	. . .
	break;
case 4:
	. . .
	break;
default:
	// bad input
	. . .
	break;
}





3.8.6 Statements That Break Control Flow

break:中止循环

continue:结束这一次循环

